	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "See MRR 2.37, 39, note 24, and Index, 582, on Lucanus, Leg., lieut. of Cosconius in 89 (Liv. Per. 75; see MRR 2.33, 36, 37, 39, notes 21 and 24). Cf. the consilium of Pompeius Strabo at Asculum: Cichorius, RS 171-172; Criniti, L'Epigrafe di Asculum 21, 158-159. See also Wiseman, NM 238, no. 232.\n" .
